  "informal_statement": "For every integer r and natural number n, the geometric series sum 1 + r + r^2 + ... + r^(n-1), multiplied by (r - 1), equals r^n - 1.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Induction on n: peel the last term r^k with Finset.sum_range_succ, distribute (r - 1) over the sum via add_mul, apply the hypothesis, then close the resulting polynomial identity with ring.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem geom_series_sum_induction (r : ℤ) (n : ℕ) : (∑ i ∈ Finset.range n, r ^ i) * (r - 1) = r ^ n - 1",
